title: Episode #1.2
description: Jutka Vágási takes up the matter of a hungry girl. The Takács family receives a letter from the GDR. A phone is installed at the Mágenheims.

title: Episode #1.4
description: The Takács family visits relatives in Ózd. The Mágenheims' phone is stolen. A new problem arise at the Vágásis: Jutka has to be transferred to a new school.
